AI tab manager for the heavy-duty researcher. TabCrunch uses language models to help you crunch key information from your tabs.

- Organise tabs into groups;
- Get through all your open tabs faster with a comprehensive summary of each tab;
- Free your browser from tab clutter, save memory, and reduce load on your device;
- Easily find the tab you need with a quick keyword search;
- See reading time, content overlap, and language for each tab;
- Free your browser from tab clutter;
- Share tab groups and collaborate with others.
